Package com.facebook.buck.edenfs

Interface EdenClient

  • public interface EdenClient
    Client of Eden's fbthrift API that is intended to be a thin wrapper around EdenService.Client's API.

    Note that implementations of this interface are not guaranteed to be thread-safe.
